  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8099953">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8099953/" class="title-link">被神化的巨人？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8099953"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2170535/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2170535-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2170535/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">候鸟</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-09-24"
      class="main-meta">2016-09-24 21:58:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8099953_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书是有关万世枭雄凯撒的最新一本传记，原著出版于2006年。全书按照时间顺序分三部分讲述了凯撒的成长与政治上的崛起、平定高卢和征服不列颠、内战与短暂的独裁，综合各方面史料及凯撒自己的《战记》，很好地讲述了凯撒这个传奇人物的生平。全书故事性很强，文字流畅，除介绍...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8099953_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8099953_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










